title: Vayden - EP Demo CD
description:
This is a 4-song demo CD from a local Arizona band. It says on the cover, "Copying, distributing, sharing or making people listen to this music is highly encouraged." I copied it in WMA Lossless format so I can share and distribute it and now you can copy it and make people listen to it.

     1: The One You Left Behind
     2: Uniforms
     3: Elysium
     4: Anthem of the Used

If you like it, you can find out more about Vayden at

There is also a warning on the CD sleeve.
